entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: I have demonstrated my abilities as an enforcer and will likely receive additional assignments from Loruna Scathe soon.
entries.journal_entry_description: Loruna has directed me to one of her contacts in the field. This contact will have further information about this enforcement assignment.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Loruna says that she has identified an assignment that suits my talents. I will learn more from her contact in the field. Loruna can give me directions to the contact, should I need them. When I am done with my mission, I should report back to Loruna in Theed.
